 H  1.01  H.blyp-hgh.UPF
 O  16.0  O.blyp-hgh.UPF
ATOMIC_POSITIONS angstrom
 O 0.025714 -0.017989 0.111617
 H -0.445397 0.836104 -0.115546
 H 0.038047 -0.551133 -0.717445
K_POINTS
